text: 90125 is the eleventh studio album by Yes. ==Overview== The album was released on November 8, 1983 through Atlantic Records. It was the group's first studio album of new material in 3 years. ==Performance== It peaked at number 2 in France and Germany, number 3 in Canada and Switzerland, number 4 in the Netherlands, number 5 in the United States and number 16 in the United Kingdom (UK). It received a Grammy nomination for Best Rock Performance by a Duo or Group with Vocal and a Grammy Award for Best Rock Instrumental Performance in 1985. == Track listing == == References == Category:1983 albums Category:Yes (band) albums
